title: Ep - 33 - Sweet Home Oklahoma's Jennifer Welch
description:
Jennifer Welch from Bravo's breakout hit Sweet Home Oklahoma explains how the show was created, if she will ever get remarried, and how many gloves Pumps goes through in a week. Gareth Reynolds from Point vs. Point podcast reviews the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion part one. Kate discusses her love for MTV's The Osbournes and why Easter has never been the same since the year her sister's boyfriend ran over the family dog.
